<div class="title">Medical Usage</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines - Adderall</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Steve&Exact=1">Steve</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Steve. "Medical Usage: An Experience with Amphetamines - Adderall (exp13334)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 16, 2007. erowid.org/exp/13334</div>

<br/>



